``` Basic search with index and sourcetype ```
index=main sourcetype=syslog host=webserver*
| search status=500 OR status=503
| where _time > relative_time(now(), "-24h@h")

``` Eval with various functions ```
| eval
    duration_mins = round(duration / 60, 2),
    status_group = case(
        status < 200, "informational",
        status < 300, "success",
        status < 400, "redirect",
        status < 500, "client_error",
        true(), "server_error"
    ),
    is_slow = if(duration > 5000, true, false),
    request_id = md5(host . ":" . uri_path),
    event_hour = strftime(_time, "%Y-%m-%d %H"),
    tags_list = mvappend(tag1, tag2, tag3),
    payload = json_object("status", status, "host", host),
    trimmed = trim(ltrim(rtrim(message))),
    angle = atan2(y, x),
    bits = bit_and(flags, 0xFF)

``` Stats and charting functions ```
| stats
    count AS total_events,
    avg(duration) AS avg_duration,
    max(duration) AS max_duration,
    min(duration) AS min_duration,
    dc(user) AS unique_users,
    sum(bytes) AS total_bytes,
    stdev(duration) AS duration_stddev,
    perc(duration, 95) AS p95_duration,
    earliest(_time) AS first_seen,
    latest(_time) AS last_seen,
    values(status) AS status_codes,
    list(uri_path) AS paths
    by host, sourcetype

``` Timechart and chart commands ```
| timechart span=1h count by status
| chart avg(cpu_pct) over host by datacenter

``` Transaction with multiple clauses ```
| transaction session_id
    startswith="login" endswith="logout"
    maxspan=30m maxpause=5m maxevents=1000
    keeporphans=true

``` Subsearch ```
| search [search index=threats earliest=-1h | fields src_ip | format]

``` String operations ```
| eval
    lower_name = lower(username),
    upper_name = upper(username),
    name_len = len(username),
    first_three = substr(username, 0, 3),
    clean = replace(message, "\r\n", " ")

``` Multivalue operations ```
| makemv delim="," categories
| mvexpand categories
| eval mv_count = mvcount(categories)
| where mvfind(categories, "critical") >= 0
| eval sorted = mvsort(categories)
| eval joined = mvjoin(categories, "; ")

``` Table and field operations ```
| table _time, host, sourcetype, status, duration, message
| rename duration AS response_time, message AS log_message
| fields - _raw, _serial, _si
| sort - response_time
| head 100
| tail 50

``` Dedup and filtering ```
| dedup host, sourcetype sortby -_time
| where isnotnull(error_code) AND isnum(status)
| regex message="(?i)error|exception|fail"

``` Lookup ```
| lookup geo_lookup ip AS src_ip OUTPUT city, country, lat, lon
| inputlookup user_list.csv WHERE department="engineering"

``` Time modifiers in search ```
earliest=-7d@d latest=now index=main sourcetype="access_combined"
| timechart span=1d count

``` Macros (backtick-delimited) ```
| `my_custom_macro(arg1, arg2)`
| `get_notable_events`

``` Multiline comment
spanning multiple
lines ```

``` Rex and regex ```
| rex field=message "(?P<error_type>\w+Error): (?P<error_msg>.+)"
| rex mode=sed "s/password=[^&]*/password=REDACTED/g"

``` Spath for JSON parsing ```
| spath input=json_field path=data.results{}
| spath output=user_name path="user.name"

``` Eventstats and streamstats ```
| eventstats avg(duration) AS global_avg by sourcetype
| streamstats count AS event_num window=100
| where duration > global_avg * 2

``` Convert and fieldformat ```
| convert ctime(_time) AS human_time
| convert dur2sec(duration)
| fieldformat total_bytes = tostring(total_bytes, "commas")

``` Append and join ```
| append [search index=summary sourcetype=daily_report | stats sum(count) AS total]
| join type=left host [search index=assets | table host, owner, environment]

``` Top and rare ```
| top limit=20 useother=true status by host
| rare limit=10 uri_path

``` Boolean and comparison operators ```
| where (status >= 400 AND status < 500) OR (status == 503)
| eval result = if(value != 0, 100 / value, null())
| where NOT cidrmatch("10.0.0.0/8", src_ip)
| eval check = if(method == "GET" AND status < 300, "ok", "fail")

``` Number formats ```
| eval pi_val = 3.14159
| eval big = 1.5e10
| eval small = 2.3E-5
| eval count = 42
| eval pct = 99.9

``` Trig and hyperbolic functions ```
| eval s = sin(0.5), c = cos(0.5), t = tan(0.5)
| eval h = hypot(3, 4)
| eval as = asin(0.5), ac = acos(0.5), at = atan(1.0)
| eval sh = sinh(1), ch = cosh(1), th = tanh(1)

``` JSON functions ```
| eval obj = json_object("key", "value")
| eval arr = json_array("a", "b", "c")
| eval val = json_extract(payload, "data.items")
| eval valid = json_valid(raw_json)
| eval keys = json_keys(payload)

``` Cryptographic functions ```
| eval hash1 = md5(password)
| eval hash2 = sha256(token)
| eval hash3 = sha512(secret)

``` Informational functions ```
| where isbool(flag) OR isint(count) OR isstr(name)
| eval t = typeof(value)

``` Conversion functions ```
| eval n = tonumber(str_val)
| eval s = tostring(num_val, "hex")
| eval b = tobool("true")

``` Bitwise functions ```
| eval result = bit_and(a, b)
| eval shifted = bit_shift_left(x, 2)
| eval flipped = bit_not(mask)
| eval mixed = bit_xor(val1, val2)

``` Collect and mcollect ```
| collect index=summary marker="daily_report"
| mcollect index=metrics_store

``` Datamodel ```
| datamodel "Network_Traffic" "All_Traffic" search
| tstats count from datamodel=Authentication by user

``` Constants ```
| eval flag = true
| eval empty = null
| eval off = false
| where value = TRUE OR value = FALSE

``` XOR operator ```
| where condA XOR condB

``` Wildcard searches ```
error source=*access* host=web-*
| search NOT source="*test*"

``` Map command ```
| map search="search index=detailed host=$host$ | head 10" maxsearches=5

``` Predict and trendline ```
| predict duration AS predicted_duration algorithm=LLP holdback=24
| trendline sma5(count) AS trend

``` Geostats ```
| iplocation src_ip
| geostats latfield=lat longfield=lon count by country

``` Fill operations ```
| fillnull value="N/A" field1, field2
| filldown field3

``` Format and outputcsv ```
| format maxresults=100
| outputcsv report_output.csv

``` Set operations ```
| set diff [search index=a | table host] [search index=b | table host]

``` Bin / bucket ```
| bin _time span=5m
| bucket duration bins=10

``` REST and inputcsv ```
| rest /services/saved/searches
| inputcsv my_saved_results.csv
